data.description: Discover an exquisite beauty nestled near a cul-de-sac, beckoning with serene charm in a well-maintained neighborhood.  This captivating gem boasts 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, each offering comfort in spacious luxury.  The owner's suite, situated upstairs, provides a haven of relaxation, complemented by a catwalk overlooking the inviting two-story family room that bathes in natural light.  The heart of this home, the updated kitchen, adorned with stainless steel appliances, beckons for cherished family moments.  Versatility abounds with separate living and dining spaces, perfect for both entertainment and tranquility.  Stepping outside reveals a vast fenced-in backyard, complete with an expansive patio, ideal for gatherings of any size or quite family moments alike.  Warmth, elegance, and comfort seamlessly unite in the remarkable haven.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beauty your new home where comfort and style converge for an exceptional living experience!
